113 /* All DSS exception events signalled directly through DSS2MSS SW1 ISR, these are
114  exception events that happen in the ISRs of DSS such as missing processing deadlines
115  for chirp or frame for which DSS cannot use the mailbox path to communicate with MSS
116  because of the urgent nature of the events. DSP will do a local assert in its
117  ISR after signalling the exception to the MSS. */
118 #define MMWDEMO_DSS_EXCEPTION_EVENTS (MMWDEMO_DSS_CHIRP_PROC_DEADLINE_MISS_EVT | \
119  MMWDEMO_DSS_FRAME_PROC_DEADLINE_MISS_EVT )
